    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a Gradation 3 requirement due to single loading condition tested; this gap is accepted given the COU scope is limited to compression-bending and is mitigated by the sensitivity analysis validation result. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
